high_descs: Turn left  to walk past the end of the kitchen island and continue to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Step left to stand centered with the sink.
Use the knife to slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn to face the stove.
Place the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn back around to face the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right and carry the tomato slice to the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave above the stove and then remove once heated.
Turn right, and move to the trash bin to the right of the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a slice of heated tomato in the trash bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the right of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife in front of the toaster.
Move over left to the front of the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn right to face the stove.
Place the gray knife on the edge of the counter on the left.
Turn left to face the sink.
Pick up one slice of the tomato from the sink.
Turn right and go to the microwave above the stove.
Remove the tomato slice after heating it in the microwave.
Turn right and go to the trash can on the right side of the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a heated slice of tomato.
